    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-07-28T19:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-07-28T19:00:00-05:00" n="732"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d732">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">124.936/7–2848: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-07-28T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 28, 1948—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1083. Dept has received copy Operation Plan 103 (Embdesp 217 May 6) and copies
                    local emergency plans Peiping and Tientsin.<note n="63" xml:id="d732fn63">None
                        printed.</note> Prior submission protection and evacuation question for
                    consideration SANACC, Dept desires receive copies local plans all posts as well
                    as integrated plan (Dept Cirair Apr 6, Para 5). Pls report present status these
                    plans and approximate dates completion and forwarding Dept.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Marshall</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
